{
  "video_id": "OF2N6a3t6uY",
  "title": "Sarah Kaminsky: My father the forger",
  "es": 1,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 0.0,
      "end_time": 7000.0,
      "text": "Translator: federica bonaldi Reviewer: Thomas VANDENBOGAERDE"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 16260.000000000002,
      "end_time": 19176.0,
      "text": "I am the daughter of a forger,"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 19176.0,
      "end_time": 21121.0,
      "text": "not just any forger ..."
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 21121.0,
      "end_time": 24370.0,
      "text": "When you hear the word \"forger,\" you often understand \"mercenary.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 24380.0,
      "end_time": 27560.0,
      "text": "You understand \"forged currency,\" \"forged pictures.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 27560.0,
      "end_time": 29872.0,
      "text": "My father is no such man."
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 29872.0,
      "end_time": 31600.0,
      "text": "For 30 years of his life,"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 31600.0,
      "end_time": 33762.0,
      "text": "he made false papers --"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 33762.0,
      "end_time": 35707.0,
      "text": "never for himself, always for other people,"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 35707.0,
      "end_time": 39596.0,
      "text": "and to come to the aid of the persecuted and the oppressed."
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 39596.0,
      "end_time": 41760.0,
      "text": "Let me introduce him."
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 41760.0,
      "end_time": 44760.0,
      "text": "Here is my father at age 19."
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 44760.0,
      "end_time": 48760.0,
      "text": "It all began for him during World War II,"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 48760.0,
      "end_time": 50760.0,
      "text": "when at age 17 he found himself thrust"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 50760.0,
      "end_time": 52460.0,
      "text": "into a forged documents workshop."
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 52460.0,
      "end_time": 56960.0,
      "text": "He quickly became the false papers expert of the Resistance."
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 56960.0,
      "end_time": 58760.0,
      "text": "And it&#39;s not a banal story --"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 58760.0,
      "end_time": 61760.0,
      "text": "after the liberation he continued"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 61760.0,
      "end_time": 64860.0,
      "text": "to make false papers until the &#39;70s."
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 64860.0,
      "end_time": 66510.0,
      "text": "When I was a child"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 66510.0,
      "end_time": 68658.0,
      "text": "I knew nothing about this, of course."
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 68658.0,
      "end_time": 71160.0,
      "text": "This is me in the middle making faces."
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 71160.0,
      "end_time": 73491.0,
      "text": "I grew up in the Paris suburbs"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 73492.0,
      "end_time": 77381.0,
      "text": "and I was the youngest of three children."
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 77381.0,
      "end_time": 80271.0,
      "text": "I had a \"normal\" dad like everybody else,"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 80271.0,
      "end_time": 82216.0,
      "text": "apart from the fact that he was 30 years older than ..."
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 82216.0,
      "end_time": 86104.0,
      "text": "well, he was basically old enough to be my grandfather."
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 86105.0,
      "end_time": 89600.0,
      "text": "Anyway, he was a photographer and a street educator,"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 89600.0,
      "end_time": 92660.0,
      "text": "and he always taught us to obey the law very strictly."
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 92660.0,
      "end_time": 94960.0,
      "text": "And, of course, he never talked about his past life"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 94960.0,
      "end_time": 97160.0,
      "text": "when he was a forger."
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 97160.0,
      "end_time": 99719.0,
      "text": "There was, however, an incident I&#39;m going to tell you about,"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 99719.0,
      "end_time": 102636.0,
      "text": "that perhaps could have led me suspect something."
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 102636.0,
      "end_time": 105553.0,
      "text": "I was in high school and got a bad grade,"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 105553.0,
      "end_time": 107497.0,
      "text": "a rare event for me,"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 107498.0,
      "end_time": 110443.0,
      "text": "so I decided to hide it from my parents."
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 110443.0,
      "end_time": 114332.0,
      "text": "In order to do that, I set out to forge their signature."
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 114332.0,
      "end_time": 117460.0,
      "text": "I started working on my mother&#39;s signature,"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 117460.0,
      "end_time": 120166.0,
      "text": "because my father&#39;s is absolutely impossible to forge."
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 120167.0,
      "end_time": 123840.0,
      "text": "So, I got working. I took some sheets of paper"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 123840.0,
      "end_time": 126100.0,
      "text": "and started practicing, practicing, practicing,"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 126200.0,
      "end_time": 127946.0,
      "text": "until I reached what I thought was a steady hand,"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 127946.0,
      "end_time": 129889.0,
      "text": "and went into action."
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 129889.99999999999,
      "end_time": 132260.0,
      "text": "Later, while checking my school bag,"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 132260.0,
      "end_time": 135751.0,
      "text": "my mother got hold of my school assignment and immediately saw that the signature was forged."
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 135752.0,
      "end_time": 137697.0,
      "text": "She yelled at me like she never had before."
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 137697.0,
      "end_time": 140614.0,
      "text": "I went to hide in my bedroom, under the blankets,"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 140614.0,
      "end_time": 143559.0,
      "text": "and then I waited for my father to come back from work"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 143559.0,
      "end_time": 145448.0,
      "text": "with, one could say, much apprehension."
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 145449.0,
      "end_time": 147421.0,
      "text": "I heard him come in."
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 147421.0,
      "end_time": 151338.0,
      "text": "I remained under the blankets. He entered my room,"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 151338.0,
      "end_time": 153283.0,
      "text": "sat on the corner of the bed,"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 153283.0,
      "end_time": 156172.0,
      "text": "and he was silent, so I pulled the blanket from my head,"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 156173.0,
      "end_time": 159900.0,
      "text": "and when he saw me he started laughing."
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 159900.0,
      "end_time": 162700.0,
      "text": "He was laughing so hard, he could not stop and he was holding my assignment in his hand."
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 162700.0,
      "end_time": 166360.0,
      "text": "Then he said, \"But really, Sarah, you could have worked harder! Can&#39;t you see it&#39;s really too small?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 166360.0,
      "end_time": 172260.0,
      "text": "Indeed, it&#39;s rather small."
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 172260.0,
      "end_time": 174260.0,
      "text": "I was born in Algeria."
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 174260.0,
      "end_time": 177565.0,
      "text": "There I would hear people say my father was a \"moudjahid\""
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 177565.0,
      "end_time": 178760.0,
      "text": "and that means \"fighter.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 178760.0,
      "end_time": 183344.0,
      "text": "Later on, in France, I loved eavesdropping on grownups&#39; conversations,"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 183344.0,
      "end_time": 186261.0,
      "text": "and I would hear all sorts of stories about my father&#39;s previous life,"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 186261.0,
      "end_time": 189179.0,
      "text": "especially that he had \"done\" World War II,"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 189179.0,
      "end_time": 191123.0,
      "text": "that he had \"done\" the Algerian war."
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 191123.0,
      "end_time": 194410.0,
      "text": "And in my head I would be thinking that \"doing\" a war meant being a soldier."
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 194410.0,
      "end_time": 197958.0,
      "text": "But knowing my father, and how he kept saying that he was a pacifist and non-violent,"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 197958.0,
      "end_time": 201260.0,
      "text": "I found it very hard to picture him with a helmet and gun."
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 201260.0,
      "end_time": 203260.0,
      "text": "And indeed, I was very far from the mark."
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 203260.0,
      "end_time": 206459.0,
      "text": "One day, while my father was working on a file"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 206460.0,
      "end_time": 209626.0,
      "text": "for us to obtain French nationality,"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 209626.0,
      "end_time": 211571.0,
      "text": "I happened to see some documents"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 211571.0,
      "end_time": 213988.0,
      "text": "that caught my attention."
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 213988.0,
      "end_time": 215660.0,
      "text": "These are real!"
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 215660.0,
      "end_time": 218378.0,
      "text": "These are mine, I was born an Argentinean."
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 218378.0,
      "end_time": 220160.0,
      "text": "But the document I happened to see"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 220160.0,
      "end_time": 222267.0,
      "text": "that would help us build a case for the authorities"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 222267.0,
      "end_time": 224960.0,
      "text": "was a document from the army"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 224960.0,
      "end_time": 228129.0,
      "text": "that thanked my father for his work"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 228129.0,
      "end_time": 230480.0,
      "text": "on behalf of the secret services."
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 230480.0,
      "end_time": 232965.0,
      "text": "And then, suddenly, I went \"wow!\""
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 232965.0,
      "end_time": 234660.0,
      "text": "My father, a secret agent?"
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 234660.0,
      "end_time": 236826.0,
      "text": "It was very James Bond."
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 236826.0,
      "end_time": 241715.0,
      "text": "I wanted to ask him questions, which he didn&#39;t answer."
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 241715.0,
      "end_time": 244660.0,
      "text": "And later, I told myself that"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 244660.0,
      "end_time": 247260.0,
      "text": "one day I would have to question him."
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 247260.0,
      "end_time": 249411.0,
      "text": "And then I became a mother and had a son,"
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 249411.0,
      "end_time": 252560.0,
      "text": "and finally decided it was time -- that he absolutely had to talk to us."
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 252560.0,
      "end_time": 254560.0,
      "text": "I had become a mother"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 254560.0,
      "end_time": 256560.0,
      "text": "and he was celebrating his 77th birthday,"
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 256560.0,
      "end_time": 258860.0,
      "text": "and suddenly I was very, very afraid."
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 258860.0,
      "end_time": 261108.0,
      "text": "I feared he&#39;d go"
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 261108.0,
      "end_time": 263530.0,
      "text": "and take his silences with him,"
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 263530.0,
      "end_time": 264997.0,
      "text": "and take his secrets with him."
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 264997.0,
      "end_time": 267360.0,
      "text": "I managed to convince him that it was important for us,"
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 267360.0,
      "end_time": 268887.0,
      "text": "but possibly also for other people"
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 268887.0,
      "end_time": 270832.0,
      "text": "that he shared his story."
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 270832.0,
      "end_time": 272776.0,
      "text": "He decided to tell it to me"
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 272776.0,
      "end_time": 274600.0,
      "text": "and I made a book,"
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 274600.0,
      "end_time": 276666.0,
      "text": "from which I&#39;m going to read you some excerpts later."
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 276666.0,
      "end_time": 279582.0,
      "text": "So, his story. My father was born in Argentina."
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 279583.0,
      "end_time": 281528.0,
      "text": "His parents were of Russian descent."
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 281528.0,
      "end_time": 285445.0,
      "text": "The whole family came to settle in France in the &#39;30s."
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 285446.0,
      "end_time": 290260.0,
      "text": "His parents were Jewish, Russian and above all, very poor."
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 290260.0,
      "end_time": 293260.0,
      "text": "So at the age of 14 my father had to work."
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 293260.0,
      "end_time": 294460.0,
      "text": "And with his only diploma,"
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 294460.0,
      "end_time": 295760.0,
      "text": "his primary education certificate,"
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 295760.0,
      "end_time": 298260.0,
      "text": "he found himself working at a dyer - dry cleaner."
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 298260.0,
      "end_time": 301460.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s where he discovered something totally magical,"
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 301460.0,
      "end_time": 303260.0,
      "text": "and when he talks about it, it&#39;s fascinating --"
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 303260.0,
      "end_time": 306600.0,
      "text": "it&#39;s the magic of dyeing chemistry."
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 306600.0,
      "end_time": 307860.0,
      "text": "During that time the war was happening"
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 307860.0,
      "end_time": 310727.0,
      "text": "and his mother was killed when he was 15."
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 310728.0,
      "end_time": 313260.0,
      "text": "This coincided with the time when"
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 313260.0,
      "end_time": 315260.0,
      "text": "he threw himself body and soul into chemistry"
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 315260.0,
      "end_time": 317960.0,
      "text": "because it was the only consolation for his sadness."
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 317960.0,
      "end_time": 321423.0,
      "text": "All day he would ask many questions to his boss"
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 321424.0,
      "end_time": 324260.0,
      "text": "to learn, to accumulate more and more knowledge,"
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 324260.0,
      "end_time": 325760.0,
      "text": "and at night, when no one was looking,"
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 325760.0,
      "end_time": 327960.0,
      "text": "he&#39;d put his experience to practice."
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 327960.0,
      "end_time": 333600.0,
      "text": "He was mostly interested in ink bleaching."
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 333600.0,
      "end_time": 335260.0,
      "text": "All this to tell you"
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 335260.0,
      "end_time": 337760.0,
      "text": "that if my father became a forger, actually,"
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 337760.0,
      "end_time": 339760.0,
      "text": "it was almost by accident."
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 339760.0,
      "end_time": 342260.0,
      "text": "His family was Jewish, so they were hounded."
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 342260.0,
      "end_time": 345260.0,
      "text": "Finally they were all arrested and taken to the Drancy camp"
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 345260.0,
      "end_time": 348460.0,
      "text": "and they managed to get out at the last minute thanks to their Argentinean papers."
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 348460.0,
      "end_time": 349594.0,
      "text": "Well, they were out,"
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 349596.0,
      "end_time": 352512.0,
      "text": "but they were always in danger. The big \"Jew\" stamp was still on their papers."
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 352513.0,
      "end_time": 355760.0,
      "text": "It was my grandfather who decided they needed false documents."
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 355760.0,
      "end_time": 359260.0,
      "text": "My father had been instilled with such respect for the law"
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 359260.0,
      "end_time": 361260.0,
      "text": "that although he was being persecuted,"
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 361260.0,
      "end_time": 363260.0,
      "text": "he&#39;d never thought of false papers."
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 363260.0,
      "end_time": 366260.0,
      "text": "But it was he who went to meet a man from the Resistance."
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 366260.0,
      "end_time": 368760.0,
      "text": "In those times documents had hard covers,"
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 368760.0,
      "end_time": 370260.0,
      "text": "they were filled in by hand,"
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 370260.0,
      "end_time": 373260.0,
      "text": "and they stated your job."
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 373260.0,
      "end_time": 375460.0,
      "text": "In order to survive, he needed"
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 375460.0,
      "end_time": 377460.0,
      "text": "to be working. He asked the man"
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 377460.0,
      "end_time": 379260.0,
      "text": "to write \"dyer.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 379260.0,
      "end_time": 382260.0,
      "text": "Suddenly the man looked very, very interested."
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 382260.0,
      "end_time": 385460.0,
      "text": "As a \"dyer,\" do you know how to bleach ink marks?"
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 385460.0,
      "end_time": 387760.0,
      "text": "Of course he knew."
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 387760.0,
      "end_time": 389560.0,
      "text": "And suddenly the man started explaining that"
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 389560.0,
      "end_time": 392260.0,
      "text": "actually the whole Resistance had a huge problem:"
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 392260.0,
      "end_time": 394860.0,
      "text": "even the top experts"
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 394860.0,
      "end_time": 398460.0,
      "text": "could not manage to bleach an ink, called \"indelible,\""
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 398460.0,
      "end_time": 400659.0,
      "text": "the \"Waterman\" blue ink."
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 400660.0,
      "end_time": 404560.0,
      "text": "And my father immediately replied that he knew exactly"
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 404560.0,
      "end_time": 405760.0,
      "text": "how to bleach it."
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 405760.0,
      "end_time": 408960.0,
      "text": "Now, of course, the man was very impressed with this young man of 17"
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 408960.0,
      "end_time": 412760.0,
      "text": "who could immediately give him the formula, so he recruited him."
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 412760.0,
      "end_time": 415760.0,
      "text": "And actually, without knowing it, my father had invented something"
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 415760.0,
      "end_time": 418409.0,
      "text": "we can find in every schoolchild&#39;s pencil case:"
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 418410.0,
      "end_time": 421260.0,
      "text": "the so-called \"correction pen.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 421760.0,
      "end_time": 426760.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 427260.0,
      "end_time": 428659.0,
      "text": "But it was only the beginning."
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 428660.0,
      "end_time": 430260.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s my father."
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 430260.0,
      "end_time": 431760.0,
      "text": "As soon as he got to the lab,"
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 431760.0,
      "end_time": 433159.0,
      "text": "even though he was the youngest,"
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 433160.0,
      "end_time": 436600.0,
      "text": "he immediately saw that there was a problem with the making of forged documents."
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 436600.0,
      "end_time": 438960.0,
      "text": "All the movements stopped at falsifying."
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 438960.0,
      "end_time": 441560.0,
      "text": "But demand was ever-growing"
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 441560.0,
      "end_time": 444160.0,
      "text": "and it was difficult to tamper with existing documents."
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 444160.0,
      "end_time": 445660.0,
      "text": "He told himself it was necessary to make them from scratch."
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 445660.0,
      "end_time": 448460.0,
      "text": "He started a press. He started photoengraving."
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 448460.0,
      "end_time": 450600.0,
      "text": "He started making rubber stamps."
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 450600.0,
      "end_time": 451860.0,
      "text": "He started inventing all kind of things --"
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 451860.0,
      "end_time": 455260.0,
      "text": "with some materials he invented a centrifuge using a bicycle wheel."
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 455260.0,
      "end_time": 457260.0,
      "text": "Anyway, he had to do all this"
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 457260.0,
      "end_time": 460600.0,
      "text": "because he was completely obsessed with output."
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 460600.0,
      "end_time": 462260.0,
      "text": "He had made a simple calculation:"
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 462260.0,
      "end_time": 465360.0,
      "text": "In one hour he could make 30 forged documents."
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 465360.0,
      "end_time": 469760.0,
      "text": "If he slept one hour, 30 people would die."
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 469760.0,
      "end_time": 472760.0,
      "text": "This sense of"
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 472760.0,
      "end_time": 475960.0,
      "text": "responsibility for other people&#39;s lives when he was just 17 --"
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 475960.0,
      "end_time": 478960.0,
      "text": "and also his guilt for being a survivor,"
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 478960.0,
      "end_time": 482560.0,
      "text": "since he had escaped the camp when his friends had not --"
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 482560.0,
      "end_time": 484812.0,
      "text": "stayed with him all his life."
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 484813.0,
      "end_time": 487729.0,
      "text": "And this is maybe what explains why, for 30 years,"
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 487731.0,
      "end_time": 490360.0,
      "text": "he continued to make false papers"
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 490360.0,
      "end_time": 492660.0,
      "text": "at the expense of all kinds of sacrifices."
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 492660.0,
      "end_time": 493560.0,
      "text": "I&#39;d like to talk about those sacrifices,"
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 493560.0,
      "end_time": 495460.0,
      "text": "because there were many."
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 495460.0,
      "end_time": 497960.0,
      "text": "There were obviously financial sacrifices"
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 497960.0,
      "end_time": 499760.0,
      "text": "because he always refused to be paid."
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 499760.0,
      "end_time": 502460.0,
      "text": "To him, being paid would have meant being a mercenary."
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 502460.0,
      "end_time": 504600.0,
      "text": "If he had accepted payment,"
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 504600.0,
      "end_time": 505860.0,
      "text": "he wouldn&#39;t be able to say \"yes\" or \"no\""
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 505860.0,
      "end_time": 508260.0,
      "text": "depending on what he deemed a just or unjust cause."
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 508260.0,
      "end_time": 510159.0,
      "text": "So he was a photographer by day,"
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 510160.0,
      "end_time": 511760.0,
      "text": "and a forger by night for 30 years."
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 511760.0,
      "end_time": 513760.0,
      "text": "He was broke all of the time."
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 513760.0,
      "end_time": 516760.0,
      "text": "Then there were the emotional sacrifices:"
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 516760.0,
      "end_time": 519760.0,
      "text": "How can one live with a woman while having so many secrets?"
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 519760.0,
      "end_time": 523960.0,
      "text": "How can one explain what one does at night in the lab, every single night?"
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 523960.00000000006,
      "end_time": 527260.0,
      "text": "Of course, there was another kind of sacrifice"
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 527260.0,
      "end_time": 530660.0,
      "text": "involving his family that I understood much later."
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 530660.0,
      "end_time": 533760.0,
      "text": "One day my father introduced me to my sister."
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 533760.0,
      "end_time": 537760.0,
      "text": "He also explained to me that I had a brother, too,"
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 537760.0,
      "end_time": 543760.0,
      "text": "and the first time I saw them I must have been three or four,"
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 543760.0,
      "end_time": 545560.0,
      "text": "and they were 30 years older than me."
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 545560.0,
      "end_time": 551600.0,
      "text": "They are both in their sixties now."
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 551600.0,
      "end_time": 553760.0,
      "text": "In order to write the book,"
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 553760.0,
      "end_time": 557260.0,
      "text": "I asked my sister questions. I wanted to know who my father was,"
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 557260.0,
      "end_time": 558760.0,
      "text": "who was the father she had known."
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 558760.0,
      "end_time": 562860.0,
      "text": "She explained that the father that she&#39;d had"
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 562860.0,
      "end_time": 567600.0,
      "text": "would tell them he&#39;d come and pick them up on Sunday to go for a walk."
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 567600.0,
      "end_time": 569660.0,
      "text": "They would get all dressed up and wait for him,"
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 569660.0,
      "end_time": 571459.0,
      "text": "but he would almost never come."
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 571460.0,
      "end_time": 574760.0,
      "text": "He&#39;d say, \"I&#39;ll call.\" He wouldn&#39;t call."
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 574760.0,
      "end_time": 576760.0,
      "text": "And then he would not come."
    },
    {
      "index": 212,
      "start_time": 576760.0,
      "end_time": 580600.0,
      "text": "Then one day he totally disappeared."
    },
    {
      "index": 213,
      "start_time": 580600.0,
      "end_time": 581459.0,
      "text": "Time passed,"
    },
    {
      "index": 214,
      "start_time": 581460.0,
      "end_time": 584660.0,
      "text": "and they thought he had surely forgotten them,"
    },
    {
      "index": 215,
      "start_time": 584660.0,
      "end_time": 586260.0,
      "text": "at first."
    },
    {
      "index": 216,
      "start_time": 586260.0,
      "end_time": 587760.0,
      "text": "Then as time passed,"
    },
    {
      "index": 217,
      "start_time": 587760.0,
      "end_time": 589760.0,
      "text": "at the end of almost two years, they thought,"
    },
    {
      "index": 218,
      "start_time": 589760.0,
      "end_time": 592960.0,
      "text": "\"Well, perhaps our father has died.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 219,
      "start_time": 592960.0,
      "end_time": 595260.0,
      "text": "And then I understood"
    },
    {
      "index": 220,
      "start_time": 595260.0,
      "end_time": 598160.0,
      "text": "that asking my father so many questions"
    },
    {
      "index": 221,
      "start_time": 598160.0,
      "end_time": 600959.0,
      "text": "was stirring up a whole past he probably didn&#39;t feel like talking about"
    },
    {
      "index": 222,
      "start_time": 600960.0,
      "end_time": 602560.0,
      "text": "because it was painful."
    },
    {
      "index": 223,
      "start_time": 602560.0,
      "end_time": 607260.0,
      "text": "And while my half brother and sister thought they&#39;d been abandoned,"
    },
    {
      "index": 224,
      "start_time": 607260.0,
      "end_time": 608960.0,
      "text": "orphaned,"
    },
    {
      "index": 225,
      "start_time": 608960.0,
      "end_time": 611260.0,
      "text": "my father was making false papers."
    },
    {
      "index": 226,
      "start_time": 611260.0,
      "end_time": 614760.0,
      "text": "And if he did not tell them, it was of course to protect them."
    },
    {
      "index": 227,
      "start_time": 614760.0,
      "end_time": 616560.0,
      "text": "After the liberation he made false papers"
    },
    {
      "index": 228,
      "start_time": 616560.0,
      "end_time": 619459.0,
      "text": "to allow the survivors of concentration camps to immigrate to Palestine"
    },
    {
      "index": 229,
      "start_time": 619460.0,
      "end_time": 621360.0,
      "text": "before the creation of Israel."
    },
    {
      "index": 230,
      "start_time": 621360.0,
      "end_time": 623760.0,
      "text": "And then, as he was a staunch anti-colonialist,"
    },
    {
      "index": 231,
      "start_time": 623760.0,
      "end_time": 627260.0,
      "text": "he made false papers for Algerians during the Algerian war."
    },
    {
      "index": 232,
      "start_time": 627260.0,
      "end_time": 629860.0,
      "text": "After the Algerian war,"
    },
    {
      "index": 233,
      "start_time": 629860.0,
      "end_time": 632460.0,
      "text": "at the heart of the international resistance movements,"
    },
    {
      "index": 234,
      "start_time": 632460.0,
      "end_time": 634160.0,
      "text": "his name circulated"
    },
    {
      "index": 235,
      "start_time": 634160.0,
      "end_time": 636459.0,
      "text": "and the whole world came knocking at his door."
    },
    {
      "index": 236,
      "start_time": 636460.0,
      "end_time": 639960.0,
      "text": "In Africa there were countries fighting for their independence:"
    },
    {
      "index": 237,
      "start_time": 639960.0,
      "end_time": 642960.0,
      "text": "Guinea, Guinea-Bissau, Angola."
    },
    {
      "index": 238,
      "start_time": 642960.0,
      "end_time": 647460.0,
      "text": "And then my father connected with Nelson Mandela&#39;s anti-apartheid party."
    },
    {
      "index": 239,
      "start_time": 647460.0,
      "end_time": 650960.0,
      "text": "He made false papers for persecuted black South Africans."
    },
    {
      "index": 240,
      "start_time": 650960.0,
      "end_time": 652760.0,
      "text": "There was also Latin America."
    },
    {
      "index": 241,
      "start_time": 652760.0,
      "end_time": 655460.0,
      "text": "My father helped those who resisted dictatorships"
    },
    {
      "index": 242,
      "start_time": 655460.0,
      "end_time": 657360.0,
      "text": "in the Dominican Republic, Haiti,"
    },
    {
      "index": 243,
      "start_time": 657360.0,
      "end_time": 663460.0,
      "text": "and then it was the turn of Brazil, Argentina, Venezuela, El Salvador, Nicaragua,"
    },
    {
      "index": 244,
      "start_time": 663460.0,
      "end_time": 669600.0,
      "text": "Colombia, Peru, Uruguay, Chile and Mexico."
    },
    {
      "index": 245,
      "start_time": 669600.0,
      "end_time": 670760.0,
      "text": "Then there was the Vietnam War."
    },
    {
      "index": 246,
      "start_time": 670760.0,
      "end_time": 673600.0,
      "text": "My father made false papers for the American deserters"
    },
    {
      "index": 247,
      "start_time": 673600.0,
      "end_time": 676260.0,
      "text": "who did not wish to take up arms against the Vietnamese."
    },
    {
      "index": 248,
      "start_time": 676260.0,
      "end_time": 678260.0,
      "text": "Europe was not spared either."
    },
    {
      "index": 249,
      "start_time": 678260.0,
      "end_time": 680401.0,
      "text": "My father made false papers for the dissidents"
    },
    {
      "index": 250,
      "start_time": 680402.0,
      "end_time": 684160.0,
      "text": "against Franco in Spain, Salazar in Portugal,"
    },
    {
      "index": 251,
      "start_time": 684160.0,
      "end_time": 689151.0,
      "text": "against the colonels&#39; dictatorship in Greece,"
    },
    {
      "index": 252,
      "start_time": 689153.0,
      "end_time": 690860.0,
      "text": "and even in France."
    },
    {
      "index": 253,
      "start_time": 690860.0,
      "end_time": 694140.0,
      "text": "There, just once, it happened in May of 1968."
    },
    {
      "index": 254,
      "start_time": 694150.0,
      "end_time": 696660.0,
      "text": "My father watched, benevolently, of course,"
    },
    {
      "index": 255,
      "start_time": 696660.0,
      "end_time": 699459.0,
      "text": "the demonstrations of the month of May,"
    },
    {
      "index": 256,
      "start_time": 699460.0,
      "end_time": 701760.0,
      "text": "but his heart was elsewhere, and so was his time"
    },
    {
      "index": 257,
      "start_time": 701760.0,
      "end_time": 705260.0,
      "text": "because he had over 15 countries to serve."
    },
    {
      "index": 258,
      "start_time": 705260.0,
      "end_time": 707628.0,
      "text": "Once, though, he agreed to make false papers"
    },
    {
      "index": 259,
      "start_time": 707629.0,
      "end_time": 709572.0,
      "text": "for someone you might recognize."
    },
    {
      "index": 260,
      "start_time": 709573.0,
      "end_time": 712489.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 261,
      "start_time": 712490.0,
      "end_time": 714110.0,
      "text": "He was much younger in those days,"
    },
    {
      "index": 262,
      "start_time": 714110.0,
      "end_time": 716260.0,
      "text": "and my father agreed to make false papers"
    },
    {
      "index": 263,
      "start_time": 716260.0,
      "end_time": 719295.0,
      "text": "to enable him to come back and speak at a meeting."
    },
    {
      "index": 264,
      "start_time": 719297.0,
      "end_time": 724260.0,
      "text": "He told me that those false papers were the most media-relevant"
    },
    {
      "index": 265,
      "start_time": 724260.0,
      "end_time": 727760.0,
      "text": "and the least useful he&#39;d had to make in all his life."
    },
    {
      "index": 266,
      "start_time": 727760.0,
      "end_time": 729260.0,
      "text": "But, he agreed to do it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 267,
      "start_time": 729260.0,
      "end_time": 732660.0,
      "text": "even though Daniel Cohn-Bendit&#39;s life was not in danger,"
    },
    {
      "index": 268,
      "start_time": 732660.0,
      "end_time": 734853.0,
      "text": "just because"
    },
    {
      "index": 269,
      "start_time": 734855.0,
      "end_time": 736260.0,
      "text": "it was a good opportunity"
    },
    {
      "index": 270,
      "start_time": 736260.0,
      "end_time": 738744.0,
      "text": "to mock the authorities,"
    },
    {
      "index": 271,
      "start_time": 738745.0,
      "end_time": 741760.0,
      "text": "and to show them that there&#39;s nothing more porous than borders --"
    },
    {
      "index": 272,
      "start_time": 741760.0,
      "end_time": 746260.0,
      "text": "and that ideas have no borders."
    },
    {
      "index": 273,
      "start_time": 746260.0,
      "end_time": 748260.0,
      "text": "All my childhood,"
    },
    {
      "index": 274,
      "start_time": 748260.0,
      "end_time": 752357.0,
      "text": "while my friends&#39; dads would tell them Grimm&#39;s fairy tales,"
    },
    {
      "index": 275,
      "start_time": 752358.0,
      "end_time": 756247.0,
      "text": "my father would tell me stories about very unassuming heroes"
    },
    {
      "index": 276,
      "start_time": 756248.0,
      "end_time": 759164.0,
      "text": "with unshakeable utopias"
    },
    {
      "index": 277,
      "start_time": 759165.0,
      "end_time": 762810.0,
      "text": "who managed to make miracles."
    },
    {
      "index": 278,
      "start_time": 762820.0,
      "end_time": 766600.0,
      "text": "And those heroes did not need an army behind them."
    },
    {
      "index": 279,
      "start_time": 766600.0,
      "end_time": 768560.0,
      "text": "Anyhow, nobody would have followed them,"
    },
    {
      "index": 280,
      "start_time": 768560.0,
      "end_time": 771805.0,
      "text": "except for a handful [of] men and women of conviction and courage."
    },
    {
      "index": 281,
      "start_time": 771806.0,
      "end_time": 773600.0,
      "text": "I understood much later"
    },
    {
      "index": 282,
      "start_time": 773600.0,
      "end_time": 776666.0,
      "text": "that actually it was his own story my father would tell me to get me to sleep."
    },
    {
      "index": 283,
      "start_time": 776668.0,
      "end_time": 779584.0,
      "text": "I asked him whether, considering the sacrifices he had to make,"
    },
    {
      "index": 284,
      "start_time": 779585.0,
      "end_time": 781529.0,
      "text": "he ever had any regrets."
    },
    {
      "index": 285,
      "start_time": 781530.0,
      "end_time": 783260.0,
      "text": "He said no."
    },
    {
      "index": 286,
      "start_time": 783260.0,
      "end_time": 785419.0,
      "text": "He told me that he would have been unable"
    },
    {
      "index": 287,
      "start_time": 785420.0,
      "end_time": 788336.0,
      "text": "to witness or submit to injustice without doing anything."
    },
    {
      "index": 288,
      "start_time": 788337.0,
      "end_time": 791360.0,
      "text": "He was persuaded, and he&#39;s still convinced"
    },
    {
      "index": 289,
      "start_time": 791360.0,
      "end_time": 793560.0,
      "text": "that another world is possible --"
    },
    {
      "index": 290,
      "start_time": 793560.0,
      "end_time": 796560.0,
      "text": "a world where no one would ever need a forger."
    },
    {
      "index": 291,
      "start_time": 796560.0,
      "end_time": 798560.0,
      "text": "He&#39;s still dreaming about it."
    },
    {
      "index": 292,
      "start_time": 798560.0,
      "end_time": 800300.0,
      "text": "My father"
    },
    {
      "index": 293,
      "start_time": 800500.0,
      "end_time": 801760.0,
      "text": "is here in the room today."
    },
    {
      "index": 294,
      "start_time": 801760.0,
      "end_time": 805839.0,
      "text": "His name is Adolfo Kaminsky and I&#39;m going to ask him to stand up."
    },
    {
      "index": 295,
      "start_time": 805840.0,
      "end_time": 826259.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 296,
      "start_time": 826260.0,
      "end_time": 829260.0,
      "text": "Thank you."
    }
  ]
}